verbose_text: The results revealed that cell viability was significantly suppressed in response to treatment with 200, 400 and 800 muM H 2 O 2 compared with the control (XREF_FIG), while 30, 50 and 100 muM GP significantly promoted cell viability compared with the control; the increased cell viability at 30 muM GP was similar to that of 50 and 100 muM (XREF_FIG).
